flowchart TD
    Start([Tap/Click Logout]) --> Confirm{Confirm sign out?}
    Confirm -->|No| Cancel([Stay signed in])

    Confirm -->|Yes| Send[POST /api/auth/logout with Bearer token]
    Send --> FindSession{Session token exists in DB?}

    FindSession -->|Yes| MarkInactive[Set user_sessions.is_active = false]
    FindSession -->|No| NoOp[No-op on server]

    MarkInactive --> Return200[Return 200 OK]
    NoOp --> Return200

    Return200 --> ClearClient[Clear local token + user state]
    ClearClient --> Redirect([Navigate to Login])
